Instruction to build the screen shot:

1- build and open the PDF example file with 'scons'
2- In 'Interleaved Pages' mode:
   take a screenshot of the window (Command-Shift-4, then space bar),
   save is as 'shot_interleaved.png'
3- In 'Mirror Pages' mode:
   take a screenshot of the window (Command-Shift-4, then space bar),
   save is as 'shot_mirror.png'
4- run 'make_composite.sh'
